snippet.title: Wingspan - PlayStation Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wingspan is flying to PlayStation!

Discover and attract beautiful birds to your wildlife preserve in this acclaimed digital adaptation of the award-winning board game, coming soon to the PlayStation 4 & PlayStation 5 consoles!

Follow our social media to stay up to date:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MonsterCouchGames
Twitter: https://twitter.com/monstercouch
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/monstercouchgames/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@monstercouch

Wingspan Discord: https://discord.gg/wingspan
Official Wingspan Page: https://www.monstercouch.com/wingspan/
